quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  77,46,"(Gaaloy) cuna oo raaxeysta in yar. waxaad tihiin denbiilayaal."
  77,47,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  77,48,"Marka lagu yidhaahdo: Rukuuca ma ay rukuucaan{2}.",footnotes:1:. Marka lagu yidhaahdo u hoggaansama Amarka Ilaahay uma hoggaansamaan, sidoo kale waxaa lagu fasiray marka lagu yidhaahdo tukada ma ay tukadaan.,footnotes:2:
  79,37,"Ma qofkii xad gudba."
  79,38,"Oo door bida nolosha adduunkan."
  79,39,"Hubaal Naarta waa hoygiisa."
  80,34,"Maalinta uu qofku ka carari walaalki,"
  80,35,"Iyo hooyadi iyo aabbihi."
  80,36,"Iyo xaaskiisa iyo ilmahiisa,"
  83,22,"Baarriyiinta waxay ku sugnaan barwaaqo (Janno)."
  83,23,"Sariiro boqoreed korkood iyagoo ka daawan (wax waliba oo nicmooyinka jannada ah)."
  83,24,"Waxaad ka garan wejiyadooda dhalaalka barwaaqada."
  84,19,"Waxaad (dadow) mari heerar kala duwan (noloshan iyo Aakhiradaba)."
  84,20,"Muxuuse arrinkoodu yahay inaysan rumeyn xaqa?"
  84,21,"Marka Qur’aanka loo akhriyana uma sujuudaan Rabbigood (umana hoggansamaan)?"
  85,16,"Falaha Weyn ee wuxuu Doono."
  85,17,"Ma ku soo gaaray warka ciidammadii,"
  85,18,"Fircoon iyo Thamuud?"
  86,10,"Ma leh (gaalku Maalintaas) xoog ama wax u soo gargaara midna."
  86,11,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay cirka leh roobka soo noqnoqda."
  86,12,"Iyo dhulka dil-dillaaca badan (ee soo saara dhirta iyo daaqa),"
  87,7,"Wuxuu Alle doono ma’ahee, Wuxuu Og yahay waxa muuqda iyo waxa qarsoonba."
  87,8,"Waxaanu kuu fududeyn waddada sahlan (Islaamka)."
  87,9,"Ee waani, markay wax tari waanadu."
  88,4,"Gali Naar kulul."
  88,5,"Waxaa laga waraabin il kulul oo kareysa."
  88,6,"Ma laha wax cunto ah qodxo maahee."
  89,1,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay waaberiga,"
  89,2,"Iyo habeennada tobanka ah{2}.",footnotes:1:. Tobanka maalmood ee u horreeya bisha Arrafo (Xajka).,footnotes:2:
  89,3,"Iyo dhabanka iyo witirka (tirada is dheer)."